- Add user accounts/anon uploads
- Create database
  - name, size, ownership, password, date added
  - user accounts, name, 
- Settings page
  - Privacy Settings
    - Location access Settings
      - Internal Ip? What access is it allowed to have
      - External ip? Should it be allowed to create accounts, upload files, download files, etc?
      - Share who uploaded? (Always anonymous mode)
  - User Settings
    - Allow new user creation (check box)
    - Anonymous level
      - Disable login (Full Anonymous mode)
      - Enable Anonymous Account (Anonymous)
      - Disable anonymous account (No anon mode)